data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3 Bed + Office home nestled in the heart of Tacoma, where comfort & style unite. This beautiful home boasts an abundance of natural light, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere throughout. The spacious open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining & kitchen areas, making it perfect for entertaining. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring modern appliances, ample counter space & sleek cabinetry. Primary suite has plush carpeting and a luxurious ensuite bathroom. Step outside and discover an outdoor oasis that's perfect for unwinding or entertaining. The expansive backyard offers plenty of room for outdoor activities. Conveniently located to amenities. Schedule your tour today and make this property yours.
